Description: 'BiasDetect' package uses feature selection methods that can 
        account for batch effects to flag SVGs that may be strongly influenced 
        by technical factors. By examining the per-gene variance/deviance with 
        and without a batch effect, we aim to identify features that could be 
        interfering with the generation of clusters that correspond to known 
        DLPFC spatial domains.
